{"_default": {"1": {"id": "ISA.38", "bibleId": "f72b840c855f362c-04", "number": "38", "bookId": "ISA", "reference": "Isaiah 38", "copyright": "\n          \n            PUBLIC DOMAIN\n          \n        ", "content": [{"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "p"}, "items": [{"text": "In those days Hezekiah was sick and near death. Isaiah the prophet, the son of Amoz, came to him, and said to him, \u201cThe LORD says, \u2018Set your house in order, for you will die, and not live.\u2019\u201d", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.1", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.1"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "p"}, "items": [{"text": "Then Hezekiah turned his face to the wall and prayed to the LORD, ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.2", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.2"]}}, {"text": "and said, \u201cRemember now, the LORD, I beg you, how I have walked before you in truth and with a perfect heart, and have done that which is good in your sight.\u201d Then Hezekiah wept bitterly.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.3", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.3"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "p"}, "items": [{"text": "Then the LORD\u2019s word came to Isaiah, saying, ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.4", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.4"]}}, {"text": "\u201cGo, and tell Hezekiah, \u2018The LORD, the God of David your father, says, \u201cI have heard your prayer. I have seen your tears. Behold, I will add fifteen years to your life. ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.5", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.5"]}}, {"text": "I will deliver you and this city out of the hand of the king of Assyria, and I will defend this city. ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.6", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.6"]}}, {"text": "This shall be the sign to you from the LORD, that the LORD will do this thing that he has spoken. ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.7", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.7"]}}, {"text": "Behold, I will cause the shadow on the sundial, which has gone down on the sundial of Ahaz with the sun, to return backward ten steps.\u201d\u2019\u201d So the sun returned ten steps on the sundial on which it had gone down.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.8", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.8"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "p"}, "items": [{"text": "The writing of Hezekiah king of Judah, when he had been sick, and had recovered of his sickness:", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.9", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.9"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "I said, \u201cIn the middle of my life I go into the gates of Sheol.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.10", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.10"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:10"}, "items": [{"text": "I am deprived of the residue of my years.\u201d", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.10", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.10"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "I said, \u201cI won\u2019t see the LORD,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.11", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.11"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:11"}, "items": [{"text": "The LORD in the land of the living.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.11", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.11"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:11"}, "items": [{"text": "I will see man no more with the inhabitants of the world.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.11", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.11"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "My dwelling is removed,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.12", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.12"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:12"}, "items": [{"text": "and is carried away from me like a shepherd\u2019s tent.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.12", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.12"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "ISA 38:12"}, "items": [{"text": "I have rolled up my life like a weaver.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.12", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.12"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:12"}, "items": [{"text": "He will cut me off from the loom.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.12", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.12"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:12"}, "items": [{"text": "From day even to night you will make an end of me.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.12", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.12"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "I waited patiently until morning.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.13", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.13"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:13"}, "items": [{"text": "He breaks all my bones like a lion.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.13", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.13"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:13"}, "items": [{"text": "From day even to night you will make an end of me.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.13", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.13"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "I chattered like a swallow or a crane.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.14", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.14"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:14"}, "items": [{"text": "I moaned like a dove.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.14", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.14"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:14"}, "items": [{"text": "My eyes weaken looking upward.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.14", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.14"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:14"}, "items": [{"text": "Lord, I am oppressed.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.14", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.14"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:14"}, "items": [{"text": "Be my security.\u201d", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.14", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.14"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "What will I say?", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.15", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.15"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:15"}, "items": [{"text": "He has both spoken to me, and himself has done it.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.15", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.15"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:15"}, "items": [{"text": "I will walk carefully all my years because of the anguish of my soul.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.15", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.15"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "Lord, men live by these things;", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.16", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.16"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:16"}, "items": [{"text": "and my spirit finds life in all of them.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.16", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.16"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:16"}, "items": [{"text": "You restore me, and cause me to live.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.16", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.16"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "Behold, for peace I had great anguish,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.17", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.17"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:17"}, "items": [{"text": "but you have in love for my soul delivered it from the pit of corruption;", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.17", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.17"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:17"}, "items": [{"text": "for you have cast all my sins behind your back.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.17", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.17"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "For Sheol", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.18", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.18"]}}, {"text": " can\u2019t praise you.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.18", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.18"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:18"}, "items": [{"text": "Death can\u2019t celebrate you.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.18", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.18"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "ISA 38:18"}, "items": [{"text": "Those who go down into the pit can\u2019t hope for your truth.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.18", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.18"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "The living, the living, he shall praise you, as I do today.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.19", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.19"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:19"}, "items": [{"text": "The father shall make known your truth to the children.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.19", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.19"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "The LORD will save me.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.20", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.20"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "ISA 38:20"}, "items": [{"text": "Therefore we will sing my songs with stringed instruments all the days of our life in the LORD\u2019s house.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.20", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.20"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "p"}, "items": [{"text": "Now Isaiah had said, \u201cLet them take a cake of figs, and lay it for a poultice on the boil, and he shall recover.\u201d ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.21", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.21"]}}, {"text": "Hezekiah also had said, \u201cWhat is the sign that I will go up to the LORD\u2019s house?\u201d", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "ISA.38.22", "verseOrgIds": ["ISA.38.22"]}}]}], "next": {"id": "ISA.39", "number": "39", "bookId": "ISA"}, "previous": {"id": "ISA.37", "number": "37", "bookId": "ISA"}}}}